Name: MonGirl Expedition
About the game: Jack’s simple life ends on his birthday with a surprise. He ends up in an unknown land full of monster girls with a task from the Goddess herself. Will he be able to impress her? Of course, this quest won’t be simple, but Jack will meet a lot of attractive girls along the way. Will they become just friends or something more? It’s up to you! Duke it out in dynamic real-time combat, solve puzzles, meet girls, and conquer their hearts! 27 (at the moment) H scenes to unlock with more than 765 CG frames and simple, togglable animations 7 cute and gorgeous girls for you to meet and have fun with from a fluffy kitsune to a delicate kitty! Change how girls look! 17 (at the moment) different dresses, each one with unique visual art. Dynamic real-time combat instead of a turn-based system. Several endings based on your choices and your favorite girl. 165 (at the moment) game zones to loot and explore full of interesting stuff like puzzles and minigames!
